<p>It&#39;s been iPhone week. It&#39;s been server migration week. It&#39;s been tech week (in more ways than one!), and your two geeks are here, ready to roll and with a very special guest, no less! FIrst they&#39;ll talk through some of their favorite iOS 8 tips and tricks. Then it&#39;s on to a slew of your questions, including revisiting the age old question of Drobo or Synology (hint: there&#39;s no hard and fast answer here!) plus resolving John&#39;s own tech issue! Download and enjoy.</p>
